/*********Allias****************/
il va se comporter comme un clown de notre site!
    eg: chris.com : domain name
        christopher.net :allias will show the same content as the domain


/***********Redirections***********/
it will help to redirect your domain name to your target domain name
    eg: i redirect chris.com -> christopher.net
        when i will type chris.com i will automatically redirect to christopher.com

/**********Email personnalise*********/
we can create personnalise mail as :
chris.klymb.com

/***********Redirections Email*************/
it will help to redirect your mail name to your target mail name
    eg: i redirect chris.klymb.com -> christopher.klymb.net
        when i will write to chris.klymb.com mail i will automatically redirect to christopher.klymb.net


